des:
With Schneider Electric's InsightCloud skill, you can monitor off-grid and grid-tied solar and storage applications. Now with Alexa, you can quickly access critical site information from anywhere, just tell Alexa what information you need and InsightCloud skill will provide it. 

After linking your Amazon Alexa and InsightCloud or InsightMobile App accounts, you can give voice commands to Alexa.

Alexa, ask InsightCloud Connectivity status of <Your SiteName>

Alexa, ask InsightCloud Grid status of <Your SiteName>

Alexa, ask InsightCloud Generator status of <Your SiteName>

Alexa, ask InsightCloud Battery Voltage of <Your SiteName>

Note:
In order to use Amazon Alexa with InsightCloud, please follow these steps:
(1). Use InsightCloud Web portal or Download our "InsightMobile SE" app in Android or iOS app market;
(2). Register account with InsightCloud;
(3). You need to have Conext Gateway device;
(4). Configure the device in InsightCloud Web or Mobile;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android,iOS or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "InsightCloud" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "InsightCloud", and you'll be navigated to InsightCloud login page;
(9). Input your InsightCloud Web or Mobile App account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
